Spring Boot Kotlin Web app:

It is basic learning project. There were used reflection( see  ReportsController)

Tools used.
Spring Boot.
Kotlin 1.3.72
JDK version: 8.
JPA Repository.
Build tool: Apache Maven 3.6+.
Web server: Apache Tomcat.
Thymeleaf
Application container: Spring IoC. Spring Framework +.
Spring configured via Java config.
Database: H2

Steps to set-up:
1. Fill H2 with Seats - use menu bullet #1
2. Add performances - use menu bullet #2

If you need a report - use menu bullet #3